{
 "name": "RPlog_Skirmish_at_Kashyyyk",
 "title": "Skirmish at Kashyyyk",
 "summary": "The New Sith Order fleet, under Admiral Axel Vichten's full command, micro-jumps into the Kashyyyk system to bombard the Wookiee homeworld and seize a dangerous artifact being smuggled out aboard Paul Nighman's Mantaray, escorted by the pilots Ranma and Ikihsa Enb'Zik. Forewarned, the New Republic Task Group under Rasi Praddhan Cen aboard the Audacity, with Lance 'Wildman' Corbet's Rogue Squadron, scrambles to defend the planet while the volunteering Caspian commander Lynae Cassius takes the gunship Unquenchable Flame against the pirate Carrack of her old acquaintance Baron Juran Reinzhiner. Sith capital ships led by Salin Fawzy, the Viscount Aknar Koth'lryi, and pilots like Kirkland trade heavy fire with the Republic line, and Reinzhiner clamps onto the Flame to board it. Though both sides take severe losses, the artifact is jumped safely away, the Sith fleet -- harried and frustrated -- withdraws, and Kashyyyk holds in a costly Republic victory.",
